reviewText: Interesting information. Even though it covered older news of 1998 to 2010, this would be good for all interested in brain related research advances.
Very out of date. Needs to be updated.

Intriguingly significant work offering further insights into uncharted and unexploited area of our brain, so much for us to learn, which defines who we are, tells how we think, and sheds light on the next human revolution.
